{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-20",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_20_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 20 - If They Hang You",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 6,
  "page_total": 7,
  "page_start_sec": 1224.16,
  "page_end_sec": 1465.24,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.648,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 1224.16,
      "end": 1224.7,
      "text": "\"'I don't.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1224.89,
      "end": 1227.42,
      "text": "It's easy enough for me to be nuts about you.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1227.6,
      "end": 1227.7,
      "text": "you?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1228.38,
      "end": 1229.9,
      "text": "He looked hungrily from her hair to",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1229.9,
      "end": 1231.44,
      "text": "her feet and up to her eyes again."
    },
    {
      "start": 1232.68,
      "end": 1234.16,
      "text": "\"'But I don't know what that amounts to.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1234.9,
      "end": 1235.76,
      "text": "Does anybody ever?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1236.6,
      "end": 1237.44,
      "text": "But suppose I do.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1237.7,
      "end": 1238.52,
      "text": "What of it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1239.24,
      "end": 1240.52,
      "text": "Maybe next month I won't.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1241.408,
      "end": 1242.32,
      "text": "I've been through it before,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1242.58,
      "end": 1243.96,
      "text": "when it lasted that long."
    },
    {
      "start": 1244.28,
      "end": 1244.8,
      "text": "Then"
    },
    {
      "start": 1244.94,
      "end": 1245.08,
      "text": "what?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1245.9,
      "end": 1248.78,
      "text": "Then I'll remember you and I'll think I played the sap.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1249.78,
      "end": 1250.76,
      "text": "And if I did it and got",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1250.84,
      "end": 1251.26,
      "text": "sent over,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1251.42,
      "end": 1252.6,
      "text": "as I probably would,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1252.84,
      "end": 1254.88,
      "text": "then I'd sure I'd been the sap."
    },
    {
      "start": 1255.37,
      "end": 1256.02,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1256.14,
      "end": 1257.18,
      "text": "if I send you over,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1257.42,
      "end": 1258.52,
      "text": "I'll be sorry as hell."
    },
    {
      "start": 1258.8,
      "end": 1260.54,
      "text": "I'll have some rotten nights,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1260.74,
      "end": 1262.304,
      "text": "but that'll pass.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1263.62,
      "end": 1266.2,
      "text": "She raised her hands to his cheeks and drew his face down.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1267.552,
      "end": 1268.7,
      "text": "\"'Look at me,' she said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1269.14,
      "end": 1270.06,
      "text": "\"'and tell me the truth."
    },
    {
      "start": 1271.36,
      "end": 1271.94,
      "text": "Would you have done",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1271.94,
      "end": 1275.26,
      "text": "this if the Falcon had been real and you had been paid your money?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1275.82,
      "end": 1276.37,
      "text": "What"
    },
    {
      "start": 1276.74,
      "end": 1277.94,
      "text": "difference does that make now?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1279.136,
      "end": 1281.02,
      "text": "Don't be too sure that I'm as crooked as",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1281.02,
      "end": 1281.84,
      "text": "I'm supposed to be."
    },
    {
      "start": 1282.7,
      "end": 1284.68,
      "text": "That kind of a reputation might be good business,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1285.48,
      "end": 1286.98,
      "text": "bringing in high-priced jobs and",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1286.98,
      "end": 1288.5,
      "text": "making dealings with the enemy easier."
    },
    {
      "start": 1289.96,
      "end": 1290.72,
      "text": "She looked at him,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1290.72,
      "end": 1291.32,
      "text": "saying nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 1291.8,
      "end": 1294.04,
      "text": "He moved his shoulders slightly and said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1294.66,
      "end": 1295.06,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1295.26,
      "end": 1297.18,
      "text": "a lot of money would have been at least one"
    },
    {
      "start": 1297.18,
      "end": 1298.94,
      "text": "more item on the other side of the scales."
    },
    {
      "start": 1300.6,
      "end": 1302.2,
      "text": "She put her face up to his face.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1302.68,
      "end": 1304.1,
      "text": "Her mouth was partly open,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1304.2,
      "end": 1305.76,
      "text": "with lips thrust a little out."
    },
    {
      "start": 1306.5,
      "end": 1307.1,
      "text": "She whispered,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1308.0,
      "end": 1308.76,
      "text": "If you love me,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1308.88,
      "end": 1310.72,
      "text": "you'd need nothing more on that side."
    },
    {
      "start": 1312.16,
      "end": 1315.06,
      "text": "Spade set the edges of his teeth together and said through them,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1315.94,
      "end": 1317.952,
      "text": "\"'I won't play the sap for you.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1319.24,
      "end": 1320.6,
      "text": "She put her mouth against his,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1320.76,
      "end": 1321.16,
      "text": "slowly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1321.42,
      "end": 1322.64,
      "text": "her arms around him,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1322.76,
      "end": 1323.28,
      "text": "and came"
    },
    {
      "start": 1323.28,
      "end": 1324.0,
      "text": "into his arms."
    },
    {
      "start": 1325.18,
      "end": 1327.1,
      "text": "She was in his arms when the doorbell rang.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1327.85,
      "end": 1328.7,
      "text": "Spade,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1328.82,
      "end": 1330.68,
      "text": "left arm around Bridget O'Shaughnessy,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1330.86,
      "end": 1331.88,
      "text": "opened the corridor"
    },
    {
      "start": 1332.0,
      "end": 1332.16,
      "text": "door."
    },
    {
      "start": 1333.12,
      "end": 1333.8,
      "text": "Lieutenant Dundee,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1333.98,
      "end": 1335.32,
      "text": "Detective Sergeant Polehouse,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1335.44,
      "end": 1335.96,
      "text": "and two other"
    },
    {
      "start": 1336.02,
      "end": 1336.92,
      "text": "detectives were there."
    },
    {
      "start": 1337.984,
      "end": 1338.44,
      "text": "Spade said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1338.62,
      "end": 1338.752,
      "text": "Hello,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1339.5,
      "end": 1339.7,
      "text": "Tom.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1339.82,
      "end": 1340.28,
      "text": "Get them?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1341.376,
      "end": 1341.96,
      "text": "Polehouse said.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1342.6,
      "end": 1342.96,
      "text": "Got them."
    },
    {
      "start": 1343.82,
      "end": 1344.12,
      "text": "Swell.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1344.9,
      "end": 1345.18,
      "text": "Come in.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1346.272,
      "end": 1347.32,
      "text": "Here's another one for you.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1348.416,
      "end": 1349.78,
      "text": "Spade pressed the girl forward.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1350.9,
      "end": 1351.7,
      "text": "She killed Miles.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1352.8,
      "end": 1354.02,
      "text": "And I've got some more exhibits.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1354.94,
      "end": 1355.7,
      "text": "The boy's guns,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1355.88,
      "end": 1356.94,
      "text": "one of Cairo's,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1357.44,
      "end": 1359.66,
      "text": "a black statuette that all the hell was about,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1360.3,
      "end": 1362.9,
      "text": "and a thousand-buck bill that I was supposed to be bribed with."
    },
    {
      "start": 1364.32,
      "end": 1365.22,
      "text": "He looked at Dundee,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1365.34,
      "end": 1366.36,
      "text": "drew his brows together,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1366.68,
      "end": 1368.92,
      "text": "leaned forward to peer insolently into the"
    },
    {
      "start": 1368.92,
      "end": 1371.48,
      "text": "lieutenant's face and then burst out laughing."
    },
    {
      "start": 1372.72,
      "end": 1374.75,
      "text": "\"'What the hell's the matter with your little playmate,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1374.92,
      "end": 1375.12,
      "text": "Tom?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1375.7,
      "end": 1376.54,
      "text": "He looks heartbroken.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1377.1,
      "end": 1378.44,
      "text": "He laughed again."
    },
    {
      "start": 1379.488,
      "end": 1381.88,
      "text": "\"'I bet by God when he heard Gutman's",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1381.88,
      "end": 1384.21,
      "text": "story he thought he had me at last.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1385.216,
      "end": 1385.62,
      "text": "\"'Cut it out,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1385.68,
      "end": 1387.3,
      "text": "Sam,' Tom grumbled."
    },
    {
      "start": 1387.96,
      "end": 1388.84,
      "text": "\"'We didn't think—'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1389.376,
      "end": 1392.2,
      "text": "\"'Like hell he didn't,' Spade said merrily."
    },
    {
      "start": 1392.31,
      "end": 1394.88,
      "text": "He came up here with his mouth watering,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1395.5,
      "end": 1398.36,
      "text": "though you'd have sense enough to know I've been stringing Gutman.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1399.52,
      "end": 1401.44,
      "text": "\"'Cut it out,' Tom grumbled again,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1401.56,
      "end": 1403.72,
      "text": "looking uneasily sidewise at his superior."
    },
    {
      "start": 1405.02,
      "end": 1405.52,
      "text": "\"'Anyways,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1405.52,
      "end": 1406.5,
      "text": "we got it from Cairo."
    },
    {
      "start": 1407.264,
      "end": 1407.82,
      "text": "Gutman's dead.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1408.48,
      "end": 1410.64,
      "text": "The kids shot him up just before we got there.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1411.776,
      "end": 1412.48,
      "text": "Spade nodded.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1413.792,
      "end": 1416.416,
      "text": "\"'He ought to have expected that,' he said.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1419.808,
      "end": 1421.12,
      "text": "Effie Perrine put down her newspaper",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1421.12,
      "end": 1422.86,
      "text": "and jumped off from Spade's chair"
    },
    {
      "start": 1422.86,
      "end": 1424.52,
      "text": "when he came to the office at a little"
    },
    {
      "start": 1424.52,
      "end": 1426.1,
      "text": "after nine o'clock Monday morning."
    },
    {
      "start": 1427.1,
      "end": 1427.46,
      "text": "He said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1427.76,
      "end": 1428.54,
      "text": "\"'Morning,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1428.54,
      "end": 1428.96,
      "text": "Angel.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1430.08,
      "end": 1433.64,
      "text": "\"'Is that what the papers have right?' she asked.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1434.32,
      "end": 1434.82,
      "text": "\"'Yes,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1434.82,
      "end": 1435.36,
      "text": "ma'am.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1435.94,
      "end": 1438.18,
      "text": "He dropped his hat on the desk and sat down."
    },
    {
      "start": 1438.68,
      "end": 1440.6,
      "text": "His face was pasty in color,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1440.7,
      "end": 1442.76,
      "text": "but its lines were strong and cheerful,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1443.28,
      "end": 1444.02,
      "text": "and his eyes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1444.16,
      "end": 1445.18,
      "text": "though shot with blood,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1445.36,
      "end": 1445.8,
      "text": "were clear."
    },
    {
      "start": 1446.87,
      "end": 1450.26,
      "text": "The girl's brown eyes were peculiarly enlarged,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1450.3,
      "end": 1452.16,
      "text": "and there was a queer twist to her mouth."
    },
    {
      "start": 1453.08,
      "end": 1454.12,
      "text": "She stood beside him,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1454.16,
      "end": 1455.16,
      "text": "staring down at him."
    },
    {
      "start": 1455.54,
      "end": 1457.2,
      "text": "He raised his head,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1457.34,
      "end": 1457.98,
      "text": "grinned,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1457.98,
      "end": 1458.9,
      "text": "and said mockingly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1459.74,
      "end": 1461.18,
      "text": "So much for your woman's intuition.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1462.7,
      "end": 1465.24,
      "text": "Her voice was queer as the expression on her face.",
      "para_break": true
    }
  ]
}